{"tid":1850993,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(沉底po重開)黑警死全家：讓黑警與病毒connect！","createTime":"2020-01-29T23:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T01:54:35.000Z","uid":292343,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7af4ce5e66f303da911b858089acaf8a8f3a4bb6","tid":1850993,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T23:37:54.000Z","msg":"「黑警死全家」不再是口號<br />\n<br />\n信封 或者 公文袋<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好放啲用過嘅口罩入去<br />\n(如果唔想佢哋摸到質感而唔開)<br />\n或者可以<br />\n求其放啲寫字用嘅紙入去<br />\n放入去之前千祈唔好喺上面咳<br />\n或者沾啲病毒上去<br />\n<br />\n然後千祈唔好寄去黑警屋企<br />\n千祈唔好上老豆搵仔搵地址寄<br />\n<br />\n(1. 唔好放自己用過嘅口罩)<br />\n(2. 處理成件事要好小心唔好比自己接觸觸摸到病毒<br />\n或者喺紙張/信封留低指紋)<br />\n<br />\n或者任何其他可以沾有病毒嘅媒介 or 物件<br />\n都記住千祈唔好寄去黑警屋企<br />\n如果黑警屋企不幸染病<br />\n唔只會死全家<br />\n仲會返狗屋傳染比其他狗<br />\n千祈千祈唔好咁樣做<br />\n會唔會污染到其他信？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩補充 歡迎一齊討論"},{"pid":"b1d9ac38766b80599b47967443f3a84778787278","tid":1850993,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:41:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6509a9bb194e84aa1e0e235f24cabd0da2101c43","tid":1850993,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:42:12.000Z","msg":"講真就算戴左口罩同眼鏡都仲有機會中招....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848960</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"164e47d09cdc25a1b42a99c46e73690bceb53b1f","tid":1850993,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:44:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗疫保命<br />\n推翻暴政</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e04eb28848781aca30966edb7a91f47b02c748cd","tid":1850993,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"61cbb15e7a87a1bb402104f610d72427adcad5dc","tid":1850993,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"